Announcing Club.Tran Retreat numero tres en Nicaragua!  Escape the cold winter for a rugged tropical adventure in paradise February 7-12, 2024.  This 5 day trip is packed with group fitness activities like HIIT workouts, surfing, horseback riding, snorkeling and yoga.  There will be plenty of time to relax with a massage, unwind at the beach, and enjoy local culinary experiences.

We’ll be staying off the beaten path in the pacific coastal hills of Nicaragua just a 5 minute walk from the beach. The property features unique panoramic views surrounded by beautiful plants and exotic animals 🙊. There’s seating for lounging, tables for playing boardgames, and plenty of hammocks for sunbathing and stargazing.  You can choose a private or shared room (2 twins).

WHAT’S INCLUDED?
-Your transfers to and from Playa Maderas from Liberia Airport (2.5 hours each way).  Must arrive in Liberia by 1:30PM and book returning flight for 3PM or later.
-5 nights shared or private accommodations.
-Breakfast and Dinner prepared with fresh, local ingredients.
-One 60-minute massage.
-Daily group fitness activities: HIIT workouts and yoga.
-Horseback ride along the ocean (can opt out for an additional massage).
-Surfing: 2 surf lessons taught by a local expert.
-Boat day with alcoholic beverages and snacks - we’ll sail and snorkel the Pacific coast of Nicaragua.

Sign up link in bio -  refundable deposit (until 11/1). Capped at 10 people. Vamos!
